com.pilot.jword.reader
Class RTFDocumentReader.RtfDocListener

java.lang.Object
  com.pilot.jword.reader.RTFDocumentReader.RtfDocListener
Enclosing class:
RTFDocumentReader
protected class RTFDocumentReader.RtfDocListener
extends java.lang.Object

This class serves as a listener for IRun RTF Parser. IRun notifies parsed RTF objects by calling listener methods. This listener handles parse events and make necessary inserts in the document.
